## 7) Event Naming and Registry

## 7.1 Naming convention

`<domain>.<subject>.<action>`

Examples:

- `publish.asset.usd`
- `publish.anim.usd`
- `build.houdini.component`
- `texture.convert.tex`
- `tractor.job.spool`
- `storage.scan.summary`

Why:
